						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the platform of the Śiva temple outside the village.</p>						

						<p>This inscription reads from the bottom to the top.</p>						

						<p>Seems to record the death of one Peddini in a cattle raid. In characters of about the 8th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
